text:
i’ll never forget this conversation. things got real dramatic between me and the narcissist around the 4th month mark. random people were contacting me to warn me about him, i was watching him lie to his friends, i saw his temper, i saw his alcoholism, and i didn’t like how he was speaking to me at times. but i kept focusing on the amazing, flawless first 3 months of our relationship. surely, we could get back to being those head-over-heels soulmates.
.
then my friend, who had been married for a number of years at the time, reminded me this was the beginning of our relationship. if things were this dramatic and making me unhappy at four months, it was only going to get worse. and she was right. it never got better, it only got worse.
.
that’s what happens with narcissists. they reel you in fast and furious with a ton of mirroring and soulmate promises. they reel you in with over-the-top idealization and “love bombs.” they smother you with attention, affection and enmesh you into their lives. they move your relationship along quickly. you will reach milestones in your relationship in the first 3 months that healthy couples take years to reach. you will feel like you have known a complete stranger for years. you almost lose track of time when you’re with a narcissist.
.
this intensity followed by dizzying chaos is all done with intent. this is done so that you get hooked, enmeshed, and addicted early on so they can drop their mask as soon as possible. when their mask drops, the gradual abuse begins. and you’re left to feel like their personality change is your fault. and you’re left on the hook, hoping and praying for the good days to return. but they never do. not permanently at least. maybe you’ll get a good day or week, but that person never comes back. because that person you met in the beginning wasn’t real. that person was an actor playing a role. a con artist with a scam designed to trap you.
.
a telltale sign that you are dealing with a narcissist is a fast moving relationship followed by drama and chaos very early on. run if you find yourself in one of these rollercoaster relationships. things are only going to get worse. 💛🦋

text:
je rebondi sur la journée d'hier, journée dédiée aux violences faite aux femmes.
sur chérie 25 hier soir, un téléfilm très fort a été diffusé à ce sujet, suivi d'un débat, avec des femmes ayant subit des violences et d'autres qui luttent et militent pour que cela cesse.
avant cela j'avais evidement conscience que ca existait, seulement j'ai eu une prise de conscience telle que je me suis dis que moi aussi j'allais sensibiliser mon cercle, si petit soit il, pour qu'on ne banalisent pas ces actes.
aujourd'hui en france 1 femme est violée toute les 7 min, 1 femme meurt tous les 3 jours de la suite des coups de son conjoint, 200 000 femmes chaque année en france sont victimes des coups de leurs conjoints et aujourd'hui en france et partout ailleurs, nous sommes toutes susceptibles d'etre des victimes de harcèlement ou de violences physiques/ morales dans l'espace publique. 
alors aujourd'hui toi qui lis se post, si un ou "ton" homme a un jour été violent avec toi, ne met pas cela sous silence, tu n'est pas coupable de se pervers narcissique, manipulateur qui va te faire penser le contraire! n'ai pas honte de le dénoncer, car tu n'est pas en faute. 
cet homme a une emprise sur toi, il vit de ta vitalité, il te pompe, ne te laisse pas t'éteindre de l'intérieur. toi! tu mérite que l'on t'aime et ca ce n'est pas de l'amour, être un homme ne donne pas le droit de dominer sa femme, de l'insulter, ni de la battre ! 
aujourd'hui en france que tu sois victime ou témoins il y'a le 3919, alors s'il te plait compose se numéro, ces hommes ne méritent pas ton silence ! 
https://stop-violences-femmes.gouv.fr/ et 3919 
tu n'est pas seule ❤️. merci à @annececilemailfert et @mayuddha pour leurs témoignages d'hier soir, et pour leurs forces dans ce "combat" contre la violence.

@noustoutes2411 
#metoo #contrelaviolencefaiteauxfemmes #jemarchele24 #womansmarch #feminist #feminism #feministe #nosexism #violenceconjugale #nosilence #3919 #cherie25 (c'est un maquillage, j'illustre cette violence, car ça pourrait être moi, ta fille, ta mère, une femme que tu aime et estime)

text:
hier, #25novembre , était la journée  de lutte contre les violences faites aux femmes. à ce sujet, un code de détresse a été imaginé par une anglaise elle-même victime de violences, pour permettre aux victimes d’aborder le sujet discrètement.
elle propose donc aux femmes victimes de violences conjugales de se dessiner un point noir dans leur main avec un crayon à maquillage et ainsi appeler à l’aide grâce à ce signal.#blackdot 
ainsi, toutes femmes en présence de policiers ou travailleurs sociaux peut se dessiner ce point noir pour montrer sa paume de main et l’effacer simplement en se frottant la main.
alors n’hésitez pas à partager ce message pour que ce code de détresse soit connu de tous ⚠️

text:
este sábado 24 noviembre celebramos el v curso solidario contra la violencia de género, en el polideportivo de sant joan, contamos con la asistencia de más de 150 participantes, una jornada muy intensa y práctica donde  pudimos poner nuestro granito de arena contra esta lacra que vivimos hoy en día en nuestra sociedad. queria agradecer a nuestros alumnos por su ayuda y a mi amigo vicente magro magistrado del tribunal supremo por esa magnífica ponencia sobre la materia legislativa.ojalá algún día dejemos de dar estas formaciones, significará que no tendremos entre nuestra sociedad esa basuras de mierda y cobardes. y un agradecimiento especial a nuestros colaboradores que desde el principio apoyaron esta iniciativa solidaria: restaurante chapeau @taberna_chapeau obrador adhesivos @obradoradhesivos ayuntamiento de sant joan, subdelegadación de gobierno de alicante y gimnasio arena alicante @arenaalicante @jorgejuan_peterpan

text:
i've watched the qspiracy since the start.

steve bannon left the wh august last year and q appeared the following october. do you believe in coincidences?

abusing and leaking presidential information to mislead the people and benefit the hijacked party of puppets is obviously just business as usual.

however - while doing this djt with the brave bunch known as gop has willingly opened a pussy wound that anyone around the world can easily contaminate. i like to call it meddlin' with presidental blessin'. i'm not the only one who knows this opportunity and messes with the bombastic patriots - may be russia or china or mbs or antifa or me me me, a tiny quarter pounder sitting on my bed.

the whole qshow seems like a vile roleplay but instead it has become the heart of the propaganda operation that joseph goebbels would have died for. it is obvious that stuff like pizzagate™ was testing and groundwork for the 2016 election and since it proved to be very effective it is used still, today, right now.

the accompanying memes go way beyond the propaganda of nsdap. social media companies are just helpless with the fake content - there is no way they are going to risk their business by taking a real responsibility.

there is absolutely no way that gop isn't aware of what is going on - after all cambridge analytica worked for ted cruz and john bolton. the whole narrative is built on the same user data that bannon and the mercers reportedly got from cambridge analytica.

and here comes the best part. trumq is truly playing along with his tweets, gestures and words.

the bigger issue still is that requqlicans are willingly piggybacking this lunacy and abusing the faith of their fellow men while campaigning for the midterms. this is not just an insane national security risk - it's a leaking conspiracy and treason in plain sight.

text:
press release: announcing duchess international magazine print copy launch!

for immediate release
november 26, 2018

yes! we’ve got great news and we’re super excited to share!

duchess international magazine is proud to announce the launch of her maiden print edition –‘the magnificent woman’, on sunday, 9th december 2018 at the grand ibis hotel, ikeja, lagos.

the initiative, driven by the need to improve the reading experience of our esteemed readers will provide well grounded information on lifestyle, health and wellness and fashion. 
we’ve got an interesting lineup of events: enlightening discussions, networking opportunities and high profile personalities in attendance.

outstanding individuals who have done well in their chosen fields will be honoured as well.

notable speakers and guest at the event include; dr. elishama ideh, ms. yemisi jenkins mbe, ms. bisola munis and a host of others.

let’s root for each other and watch one another grow. magnificent women we all are!

don’t be left out. save the date!

text:
🍂orange the world🍂

according to  unwomen.org one in three women worldwide experience gender-based violence.

ever since i was a teenager or even younger i've been told to always carry somesort of defensespray with me and to hold  keys in my hand, when walking somewhere alone, in order to defend myself in case of an asult.  sometimes the advice, even from police have been to not walk alone at all.

unfortunately time showed that mayby i should have listened to these advices.

i wanna hold hands, carry flowers and puppies not be armoured, carrying weapons and i wanna be able to walk the earth al(l)one.

i am convinced that most people of all genders are kind and loving yet violence, abuse, sexualharassment and one in three women worldwide experience gender-based violence are undeniable facts.

it is time to change, an other world is possible. 
orange the world and #hearmetoo

peace and love .
.
.
